Date:   Fri Jan 28 19:41:37 2011 -0500

    config: replace deprecated AM_CONFIG_HEADER with AC_CONFIG_HEADERS
    
    Signed-off-by: Gaetan Nadon <memsize@videotron.ca>

commit 3776075264024af7eca93f689305d46302e88536
