commit 753fb6afb13a7ce154cd24261eadb56c3f4243c5
Author: Peter Hutterer <peter.hutterer@who-t.net>
Date:   Mon Jul 13 10:05:33 2009 +1000

    Fix segfault in XIDeviceChangedEvent wire parsing.
    
